{
  "stem": "13198.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I wasn't Dutch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Although, they liked the English.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, I was at a disadvantage.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had no home and no money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, you know, you're not very popular then in a war and Jewish as well.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So there was not much to recommend me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I never wanted to leave it again, didn't want to go on long holidays or-- there we are.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they've all-- touch wood-- turned out fine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're not great high flyers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They've not got marvelous positions or earning a lot of money, but they're decent, you know, decent people, law-biding citizens, I'd say.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They've got jobs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, they're not directors of things, but-- oh, well, Nick went to-- old Nick, the eldest, he stayed in Holland.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was very Dutch-orientated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He loved Holland.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so he went into the Dutch Navy till he got his pension and was still there to the end.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He never married.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What-- where is he?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, he's in Australia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's right, when he retired.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He retired to-- he liked Australia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's big, and he can roam.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He's-- he never-- he's one of these people who can't settle down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He's always on the move.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Steven and Carel married very nice English girls, not Jewish, of course.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And well, got families, and they've got homes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they've got jobs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they're very content and happy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they're very sweet to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all's well with the world.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was very sad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My second husband-- I'm sorry that I get mixed up with them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The second husband, David.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, I wasn't-- I had a long affair.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I will confess that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because he was married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he didn't want to divorce his wife.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
